00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:56.610
So briefly I want to
mention maybe a new frontier,

00:12:56.610 --> 00:12:59.980
which is kind of alluded
to in the first session.

00:12:59.980 --> 00:13:05.020
Advances in techniques from data
science and AI allow us to work

00:13:05.020 --> 00:13:07.420
with these logs and
digital files in new ways.

00:13:07.420 --> 00:13:10.100
So often associated
with big data trends

00:13:10.100 --> 00:13:12.500
and machine learning
