00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:52.570
of like prioritize certain kinds
of operations which extract sort

00:13:52.570 --> 00:13:54.650
of invariance about
what this façade means

00:13:54.650 --> 00:13:57.910
and you can use this for very
broad classifications of forms.

00:13:57.910 --> 00:14:01.340
So this example is not
directly archivable,

00:14:01.340 --> 00:14:03.210
but it has archivable
implications.

00:14:03.210 --> 00:14:04.730
This is a machine
vision algorithm,

00:14:04.730 --> 00:14:07.440
crawling a New York City
plan and classifying

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:10.960
by common plan outline of
thousands of buildings.

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:15.620
And so this is the -- you'll
see over time it builds actually

00:14:15.620 --> 00:14:18.560
like this phylogenetic
tree of form,

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:23.900
just from the morphological
characteristics.

00:14:23.900 --> 00:14:26.750
