this is that imagine you were

00:14:26.750 --> 00:14:29.940
to take a museum
archive of visual objects

00:14:29.940 --> 00:14:34.760
or building documents or
façade elements or 3D models

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:39.110
and ask questions about
how do these, what are all

00:14:39.110 --> 00:14:42.270
of the possible precedents
for this one object?

00:14:42.270 --> 00:14:45.210
This is a way to actually do
that by scaling up machine,

00:14:45.210 --> 00:14:48.590
scaling up human intuition into
a sort of machine platform.

00:14:48.590 --> 00:14:52.340
And so this is sort of a zoomed
out view of 100,000 buildings

00:14:52.340 --> 00:14:57.050
