00:15:00.340 --> 00:15:04.070
out you begin to see these
kind of like continents of form

00:15:04.070 --> 00:15:06.450
that emerge from
that classification.

00:15:06.450 --> 00:15:10.370
So the software draws new
charts of the past that allow us

00:15:10.370 --> 00:15:13.790
to make sense of what we build
holistically and to map all

00:15:13.790 --> 00:15:16.250
of architecture as it were.

00:15:16.250 --> 00:15:18.980
We can algorithmically
map our cultural

00:15:18.980 --> 00:15:22.370
heritage comprehensively.

00:15:22.370 --> 00:15:27.970
So these are just a couple of
the ways in which new archives,

00:15:27.970 --> 00:15:31.640
these new archives, these
files considered almost

00:15:31.640 --> 00:15:35.310
as logs allow us new ways
of addressing questions

00:15:35.310 --> 00:15:36.610
about the design process.

00:15:36.610 --> 00:15:39.610
