designers draw differently,

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:45.100
how do designers proceed
in the design process,

00:15:45.100 --> 00:15:47.220
and how does the whole catalog

00:15:47.220 --> 00:15:50.340
of built form relate
holistically.

00:15:50.340 --> 00:15:53.490
So these examples reveal new
possibilities for the use

00:15:53.490 --> 00:15:57.360
of programmatic information
generated by both the designer

00:15:57.360 --> 00:16:00.330
and the historian to
uncover the heuristic

00:16:00.330 --> 00:16:02.460
and epistemic methods of design.

