piece for at least to consider

00:50:16.540 --> 00:50:19.260
when you're archiving
a project is the fact

00:50:19.260 --> 00:50:21.750
that these transactions
are no longer happening,

00:50:21.750 --> 00:50:24.370
this super rigid kind of
hierarchical structure

00:50:24.370 --> 00:50:27.620
that we associate with
project contracts and delivery

00:50:27.620 --> 00:50:31.480
but there's actually sort of
cross-pollination happening.

00:50:31.480 --> 00:50:33.890
It's more of a web of
transactions than it is

00:50:33.890 --> 00:50:36.540
like a hierarchy, so it was
kind of, you know, handled both

00:50:36.540 --> 00:50:37.900
of those in kind of
an early fashion.

