01:00:09.690 --> 01:00:15.680
and match those component
systems to sort

01:00:15.680 --> 01:00:17.310
of plug-and-play
different configurations.

01:00:17.310 --> 01:00:20.430
And here's an example of what
an undergraduate team did,

01:00:20.430 --> 01:00:21.770
the Beijing Stadium.

01:00:21.770 --> 01:00:23.710
Turns out, you know,
there is a very --

01:00:23.710 --> 01:00:26.290
