by this guide for owners

02:13:12.830 --> 02:13:15.240
to help them organize their
information because I think

02:13:15.240 --> 02:13:18.790
if you don't ask for it in
the right way you're not going

02:13:18.790 --> 02:13:20.720
to get it in the right
way, and as we heard

02:13:20.720 --> 02:13:22.990
if you're not validating it

02:13:22.990 --> 02:13:25.740
against your requirements you
may not get what you think

02:13:25.740 --> 02:13:27.040
you're getting.

02:13:27.040 --> 02:13:30.100
So you need to know
how to structure things

02:13:30.100 --> 02:13:32.050
so you get what you want.

02:13:32.050 --> 02:13:34.800
So there's a lot of good
information out there,

02:13:34.800 --> 02:13:36.340
there's a lot of
progress being made,

02:13:36.340 --> 02:13:39.860
and it's an interesting
area to work in.

