02:16:57.910 --> 02:17:00.200
it's the Airbus's
and the Boeing's

02:17:00.200 --> 02:17:02.750
and the Daimler's of the world.

02:17:02.750 --> 02:17:08.260
But what it took for
us was since we are

02:17:08.260 --> 02:17:13.200
so concentrated was all those
big people beating the CAD

02:17:13.200 --> 02:17:15.580
vendors over the
head with a stick.

02:17:15.580 --> 02:17:19.250
We're trying to get computer
aided manufacturing vendors

02:17:19.250 --> 02:17:23.280
to implement this capability
now, that's really tough

02:17:23.280 --> 02:17:27.200
because you look at the computer
aided manufacturing and it's

02:17:27.200 --> 02:17:32.110
like Joe's Machine Shop and he
has one license of Mastercam

02:17:32.110 --> 02:17:35.910
and what's Joe going to do, what
